{"text_id":140825,"tokens":["As"," the"," academic"," year"," comes"," to"," a"," close",","," the"," topic"," of"," summer"," assignments"," has"," become"," a"," recurring"," debate"," among"," educators","."," While"," some"," argue"," that"," students"," should"," be"," given"," the"," freedom"," to"," design"," their"," own"," summer"," assignments",","," we"," believe"," that"," teacher","-","designed"," summer"," assignments"," are"," unequivocally"," more"," effective"," in"," enhancing"," students","'"," education"," and"," preparation"," for"," upcoming"," courses",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," primary"," advantages"," of"," teacher","-","designed"," summer"," assignments"," is"," that"," they"," provide"," a"," clear"," understanding"," of"," the"," curriculum"," and"," expectations"," for"," the"," upcoming"," semester","."," Students"," often"," forget"," the"," principles"," and"," concepts"," learned"," during"," the"," previous"," year","'","s"," curriculum",","," and"," teacher","-","designed"," assignments"," help"," to"," refresh"," their"," memory"," and"," prepare"," them"," for"," the"," new"," material","."," By"," providing"," a"," structured"," assignment",","," teachers"," can"," ensure"," that"," students"," are"," well","-","prepared"," to"," tackle"," the"," upcoming"," course",","," reducing"," the"," likelihood"," of"," feeling"," overwhelmed"," and"," dis","oriented"," upon"," return",".","\n\n","In"," contrast",","," student","-","designed"," summer"," assignments"," often"," lack"," the"," same"," level"," of"," rigor"," and"," focus","."," Without"," the"," guidance"," of"," a"," structured"," assignment",","," students"," may"," spend"," too"," much"," time"," on"," non","-","academic"," pursuits",","," leading"," to"," a"," lack"," of"," engagement"," and"," motivation"," when"," the"," new"," semester"," begins","."," Moreover",","," student","-","designed"," assignments"," may"," not"," align"," with"," the"," teacher","'","s"," expectations"," or"," curriculum"," goals",","," potentially"," leading"," to"," confusion"," and"," misunderstand","ings",".","\n\n","Another"," significant"," benefit"," of"," teacher","-","designed"," summer"," assignments"," is"," that"," they"," promote"," consistency"," and"," equity"," among"," students","."," By"," assigning"," a"," standardized"," assignment",","," teachers"," can"," ensure"," that"," all"," students"," have"," access"," to"," the"," same"," resources"," and"," expectations",","," regardless"," of"," their"," socio","-","economic"," background"," or"," academic"," abilities","."," This"," helps"," to"," level"," the"," playing"," field"," and"," provides"," a"," fairer"," assessment"," of"," student"," understanding"," and"," preparedness",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," teacher","-","designed"," summer"," assignments"," demonstrate"," a"," commitment"," to"," students","'"," academic"," success"," and"," serve"," as"," a"," valuable"," learning"," opportunity"," in"," and"," of"," itself","."," By"," providing"," clear"," instructions"," and"," expectations",","," teachers"," demonstrate"," their"," investment"," in"," students","'"," education"," and"," their"," willingness"," to"," support"," their"," academic"," growth",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," while"," the"," idea"," of"," student","-","designed"," summer"," assignments"," may"," seem"," appealing",","," we"," firmly"," believe"," that"," teacher","-","designed"," summer"," assignments"," are"," the"," superior"," choice","."," They"," provide"," clarity",","," consistency",","," and"," equity",","," ultimately"," enhancing"," students","'"," education"," and"," preparation"," for"," the"," upcoming"," courses","."," By"," assigning"," a"," structured"," and"," well","-","designed"," assignment",","," teachers"," can"," set"," students"," up"," for"," success",","," ensure"," a"," smooth"," transition"," into"," the"," new"," semester",","," and"," demonstrate"," their","